ifeSummary":"Quando Everhart Riehm nasceu em 1465, em Leimen, Amt Heidelberg, Baden, seu pai, Nicholeus \"Nicholas\" Riehm, tinha 33 anos e sua mãe, Fräulein Nicholeus Riehm, tinha 28 anos. Ele casou-se com Fräulein Everhart Riehm em 1490, em Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Alemanha. Eles tiveram pelo menos 1 filho e 1 filha. Ele faleceu em 1509, em Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Alemanha, com 44 anos."},"ro":{"1465–1509":"1465–1509","1470–Female":"1470–Decedată","1485–1535":"1485–1535","1490–1550":"1490–1550","1432–1490":"1432–1490","1437–Female":"1437–Decedată","1437":"1437","1535":"1535","1457":"1457","1465":"1465","1432":"1432","1485":"1485","1550":"1550","1509":"1509","1470":"1470","1490":"1490","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germania","Leimen, Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germania","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden, Germany":"Leimen, Kreis Heidelberg, Baden, Germania","of Sindelfingen, Neckarkreis, Wuerttemberg":"Sindelfingen, Kreis Böblingen, Württemberg, Germania","Leiman, Heidelburg, Baden, Germany":"Baden"},"ru":{"1465–1509":"1465г.–1509г.","1470–Female":"1470г.–Умершая","1485–1535":"1485г.–1535г.","1490–1550":"1490г.–1550г.","1432–1490":"1432г.–1490г.","1437–Female":"1437г.–Умершая","1437":"1437 г.","1535":"1535 г.","1457":"1457 г.","1465":"1465 г.","1432":"1432 г.","1485":"1485 г.","1550":"1550 г.","1509":"1509 г.","1470":"1470 г.","1490":"1490 г.","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"лимен, раин-неккар-крис, баден-вuрттембирг, Германия","Leimen, Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"лимен, раин-неккар-крис, баден-вuрттембирг, Германия","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden, Germany":"лимен, крис хиделбирг, баден, Германия","of Sindelfingen, Neckarkreis, Wuerttemberg":"синделфинген, крис бoблинген, вuрттембирг, Германия","Leiman, Heidelburg, Baden, Germany":"баден","lifeSummary":"Когда Everhart Riehm родился в 1465 г. в местности лимен, амт хиделбирг, баден, его отцу по имени Nicholeus \"Nicholas\" Riehm было 33 года, а матери, которую звали Fräulein Nicholeus Riehm, 28. Он женился на женщине по имени Fräulein Everhart Riehm в 1490 г. в местности лимен, раин-неккар-крис, баден-вuрттембирг, Германия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын и 1 дочь. Он умер в 1509 г. в местности лимен, раин-неккар-крис, баден-вuрттембирг, Германия в возрасте 44 лет."},"sm":{"1465–1509":"1465–1509","1470–Female":"1470–Ua Maliu","1485–1535":"1485–1535","1490–1550":"1490–1550","1432–1490":"1432–1490","1437–Female":"1437–Ua Maliu","1437":"1437","1535":"1535","1457":"1457","1465":"1465","1432":"1432","1485":"1485","1550":"1550","1509":"1509","1470":"1470","1490":"1490","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Siamani","Leimen, Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Siamani","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden, Germany":"Leimen, Kreis Heidelberg, Baden, Siamani","of Sindelfingen, Neckarkreis, Wuerttemberg":"Sindelfingen, Kreis Böblingen, Württemberg, Siamani","Leiman, Heidelburg, Baden, Germany":"Baden"},"sk":{"1465–1509":"1465–1509","1470–Female":"1470–Zosnulá","1485–1535":"1485–1535","1490–1550":"1490–1550","1432–1490":"1432–1490","1437–Female":"1437–Zosnulá","1437":"1437","1535":"1535","1457":"1457","1465":"1465","1432":"1432","1485":"1485","1550":"1550","1509":"1509","1470":"1470","1490":"1490","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Nemecko","Leimen, Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany":"Leimen, Rhein-Neckar-Kreis, Baden-Württemberg, Nemecko","Leimen, Heidelberg, Baden, Germany":"Leimen, Kreis Heidelberg, Baden, Nemecko","of Sindelfingen, Neckarkreis, Wuerttemberg":"Sindelfingen, Kreis Böblingen, Württemberg, Nemecko","Leiman, Heidelburg, Baden, Germany":"Baden"},"es":{"1465